{"tid":1949951,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"俄羅斯今起全國放有薪假一周","createTime":"2020-03-30T04:14:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-30T08:41:01.000Z","uid":184679,"like":26,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"e789878811c8113fec76993fba72fbb1a63fd749","tid":1949951,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T04:14:49.000Z","msg":"為了防控新冠病毒疫情蔓延，俄羅斯總統普京簽署命令，宣佈全國自3月30日起開始放有薪假一周，至4月3日結束。<br />\n<br />\n據報，普京3月25日向國民發表講話時解釋說，長假能夠降低新冠病毒在俄羅斯的傳播速度。普京隨後簽署命令，宣佈全國自3月30日至4月3日放有薪假。<br />\n<br />\n俄總統新聞秘書佩斯科夫隨後證實，本次放假一周的目的是最大限度地減少人際接觸，期間歡迎大家實施居家辦公。<br />\n<br />\n此外，俄羅斯交通和醫院、門診部、鄉村診室、藥房等醫療服務部門本星期不放假，商業網點也將繼續營業，向居民供應食品和日常生活用品。俄聯邦勞動和就業局局長指出，退休基金、社會保險基金等社保工作人員將繼續辦公，政府機關、媒體以及其他一系列領域繼續營運。<br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">https://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/wo/1735092/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82-%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B-%E4%BF%84%E7%BE%85%E6%96%AF%E4%BB%8A%E8%B5%B7%E5%85%A8%E5%9C%8B%E6%94%BE%E6%9C%89%E8%96%AA%E5%81%87%E4%B8%80%E5%91%A8</code></pre><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.zimedia.com.tw/s/8dWBFD-0\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.zimedia.com.tw%2Fs%2F8dWBFD-0&h=ec06b857&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6039467b7350c18caa92c88822b5d25a73b771fb","tid":1949951,"uid":3297,"like":26,"dislike":0,"score":26,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T04:18:34.000Z","msg":"我哋笑人唔帶口罩，佢哋笑我哋繼續返工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/as